items.name: Nescafé Ricoffy Cappuccino Sticks (8 x 23g)
items.description:
Nescafé Ricoffy is a truly South African brand whose heritage stems from the time of the French Huguenots, who originally introduced chicory-based coffee to South Africa. Since the launch of Ricory in 1952 - one of the first instant coffees to be developed; to the early 1970’s when Ricory was named Ricoffy – the brand has remained entrenched in our local coffee culture. In 2002 Ricoffy joined the Nescafé family and continues to enhance everyday moments today, tomorrow and for years to come. With a number of variants like Mild, Decaf, 2-in-1 and 3-in-1; everyone can share in the fresh percolated taste of Nescafé Ricoffy.

Peppered with flavours as diverse as our people, it is understandable that not everyone shares the same tastes in food, yet only one ingredient that is enjoyed all across our rainbow nation - maize meal. With its quick and easy preparation as well as its superior whiteness, fluffiness, texture, and taste, White Star Super Maize Meal has quickly become the leading maize meal brand that South Africans have come to love. White Star is far more versatile than an ordinary maize meal, whether served at a family braai, picnic, or cozy dinner with friends, the endless array of culinary possibilities are made likely. No matter the occasion, it is the perfect ingredient for all the good times. So come on, have a try and you will fall in love with White Star.
